    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.28.17a" />
                
                
                <opener>
                <dateline>Skryim, 5-18-'60</dateline>
                
                
                <salute>Dear Slade:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I'm ashamed and sorry!! The copies of <hi rend="underline">Easter</hi> are only now being sent, and I fear they may not reach Ithaca before you leave; but, anyway, they <del/><add>carry</add> affection.</p>
                
                <p>Alice, Lynn, and Erica are back home to stay! They've moved their horse business back, and the home is alive again!! They made good progress down south, but they (and I) had <del/> 15 horses here that were being neglected.
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.28.17b"/>
                <fw type="authorial">-3-</fw>           <fw type="curatorial"><del/></fw>
                
                and on expense. We now have some of the best horses I ever <del/> saw &#8212; one of these a stallion that you <hi rend="italic">must</hi> see.</p>
               
                <p>I'll be thinking of you out in your Pacific Paradise. Bless you, dear Brother!</p>
                <closer>
                <salute>Affectionately,</salute>
                <signed>John Neihardt</signed>.
                </closer>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">17</fw>
            </div1>
        </body>
        
